acceptance_criteria: All in_progress items are genuinely claimed or reset; every open GH issue and post-release commit maps to a pm item; every command family has a grammar-table owner under pm-n7rr and every SDK domain an owner under pm-usfg; long-term horizons extended where genuinely uncovered; zero duplicate items created
